title: Area Sports Calendar, 10/15/15
text: NOTE: Schedules provided by schools and are subject to change. High school volleyball: Casa Grande Union at Vista Grande, 6 p.m. FRIDAY High school cross country: Casa Grande Union and Vista Grande boys and girls in Titan Invitational at Crossroads Park, Gilbert, 9 a.m. High school football: Casa Grande Union at Florence; Vista Grande at Arcadia; Imagine Coolidge at Mission Heights; Maricopa at Seton; Coolidge at Fountain Hills; Tempe Prep at Santa Cruz. All games begin at 7 p.m. TUESDAY High school volleyball: Nogales at Casa Grande Union, 6 p.m.; Empire at Vista Grande, 6 p.m. Junior college volleyball: Chandler-Gilbert at Central Arizona, 7 p.m. THURSDAY, Oct. 22 High school swimming: Casa Grande Union at Florence, 4 p.m. High school volleyball: Casa Grande Union at Catalina, 6 p.m.; Vista Grande at Flowing Wells, 6 p.m.
